meanings: (글씨·그림·흔적 등을) erase, (문질러서) wipe, rub off[out], (파일 등을) delete, (줄을 그어서) strike out, cross out[of...
(기억·생각 등을) erase[wipe] (sth from one's mind), (불쾌한 기억 등을) blot out, purge (sb of sth)
(물건·짐 등을) load (sth with sth), put (a load) on sth
Verb make something wither and fall
